    "Title": "Settle a Score",
    "Description": "ECKHART SECURITY, LLC.\nCONTRACTS & DISPATCH\n\nCONTRACT TYPE: Ship Ambush\nAPPROVAL CODE = ~mission(ApprovalCode)\n\nFOR IMMEDIATE PROCESSING\n\nOne of our clients has been the victim of consistent harassment so the time has come to send a clear cease-and-desist message by taking out their prized <EM4>~mission(AmbushTarget)</EM4>.  The lowlife in question follows a fairly predictable routine making them susceptible to an ambush. We\u2019ve identified <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> as the ideal spot. It features an <EM4>emission cloud</EM4> where you can hide and power down your ship while waiting. \n\nBy the way, the <EM4>~mission(AmbushTarget)</EM4> often flies alone but is sometimes joined by a friend in a single-seat ship. Neither should give you too much trouble, but we have other contractors in the area who can lend a hand once you strike.\n\nPayment will be issued upon successful completion of contract. There\u2019s a bonus payment of <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) MG Scrip</EM4> in this for the main contractor too.\n\nThis contract is non-negotiable.\n\nThis message may contain confidential, proprietary, privileged and/or private information. The information is intended to be for the use of the individual or entity designated above.",
